HEADWORD: Siliqua
<hw>Sil"i*qua</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Siliquae</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L. See
